        "_account_id": 308,
        "name": "Amir Shehata",
        "email": "ashehata@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "ashehata"
      },
      "date": "2021-03-19 18:56:26.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThis first patch in the series prevents LNet from retrying, by making the failure a remote failure. The second patch prevents retries at the o2iblnd level.\nDo you have some data to show the delay caused by the retries @ the o2iblnd layer? IE the length of time to discover without the second patch and with the second patch.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
