      "date": "2021-03-26 15:33:12.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Amir, it took me some time to get access but I got some data, I've\n > updated the ticket.\n\nI don't see this information in the ticket. Can you make it public?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
